title: Caitlyn ganked by a terrifying Warwick.

replies.body: as a ww player 10/10 this is legit

I mean if you truly analyze the play, the menacing chase and force of flash. Taking a small break to not make himself to tired. Then the final perfect zone which obviously landed the team a "ace". This is some next level plays.
Then you grow up and have your ult with a oneshot the AD carry build.
What is this build? My friend mains ww

i don't really remember the order i build it (tends to be based off their team comp), but it something along the lines of bloodrazor, bortk, and wits end. After that I build a deadman's plate and a spirit visage to help me survive. It's rather hilarious and really good if you get super ahead cause it makes your ult deadly to anyone you mark.
